text.section:
"Creditor" means:
a lender of money or vendor or lessor of goods, services, or property rights or privileges for which payment is arranged through a credit transaction;
a successor to the right, title, or interest of the lender, vendor, or lessor;
an affiliate, associate, subsidiary, director, officer, or employee of the lender, vendor, or lessor; or
any other person in any way associated with the lender, vendor, or lessor.
